Simple Image Resizer (SIR) was created for parallel resizing images written in C++.
Project depend on Qt and libexiv2 for metadata support.

Images used in SIR was originated from different souces.
  1. Own worked:
     - sir*.{png,ico} by Rafael Sachetto
     - (un)favorite.png by Marek JÄ™dryka
  2. Third party
     - distributed under CreativeCommons Attribution 3.0 United States (CC BY 3.0) licence:
       * flip_*.png from site http://www.fatcow.com/free-icons
  3. From icon themes
     - options_*.png from Tango theme
     - other icons used in previev dialog window from Oxygen theme